#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_ocean/sea_pickle.lua:81
msgid "Sea Pickle"
msgstr "Itsas pepinoa"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_ocean/sea_pickle.lua:82
msgid ""
"Sea pickles grow on dead brain coral blocks and provide light when "
"underwater. They come in 4 sizes that vary in brightness."
msgstr ""
"Itsas pepinotxoak koralezko blokeetan hazten dira, eta argia ematen dute "
"urpean daudenean. Distira aldatzen duten 4 tamainako kolonietan etortzen "
"dira."

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_ocean/sea_pickle.lua:83
msgid ""
"It can only be placed on top of dead brain coral blocks. Placing a sea "
"pickle on another sea pickle will make it grow and brighter."
msgstr ""
"Koralezko blokeen gainean bakarrik jar daiteke. Itsas pepinotxo bat beste "
"itsas pepinotxo baten gainean jartzeak gehiago haztea eta distiratzea "
"eragingo du."

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_ocean/sea_pickle.lua:84
msgid "Glows in the water"
msgstr "Distira uretan"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_ocean/sea_pickle.lua:84
msgid "4 possible sizes"
msgstr "4 neurri posible"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_ocean/sea_pickle.lua:84
msgid "Grows on dead brain coral block"
msgstr "Hildako koral bloke batean hazten da"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_ocean/seagrass.lua:80 mods/ITEMS/mcl_ocean/seagrass.lua:105
msgid "Seagrass"
msgstr "Itsas belarra"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_ocean/seagrass.lua:104
msgid "Seagrass grows inside water on top of dirt, sand or gravel."
msgstr ""
"Itsas belarra uraren barruan hazten da, lur, hondar edo hartxintxar gainean."
